org.elasticsearch.cluster.routing.allocation.command

Class AllocateAllocationCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elasticsearch.cluster.routing.allocation.command.AllocateAllocationCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AllocationCommand

    public class AllocateAllocationCommand
extends Object
implements AllocationCommand
    Allocates an unassigned shard to a specific node. Note, primary allocation will "force" allocation which might mean one will loose data if using local gateway..., use with care with the allowPrimary flag.
